  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t知乎一篇回答，一位律师答主说，有另外的律师在法庭上因为责备书记员打字慢，所以就被书记员各种刁难，说律师说话快、听不清，还有故意漏记许多内容。而法官也袒护甚至还参与了对律师的欺凌。评论此事的律师答主及其他不少人，不是谴责书记员滥用职权、法官包庇，而是认为律师应该更加谨言慎行、不要得罪书记员。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n最可怕不是这种现象本身，而是大家觉得这没错甚至很好。虽然那律师也有过错，但是性质和程度完全不一样。严格说，这书记员已经涉嫌违纪违法，如造成恶劣后果还犯罪了。但是却完全不受罚甚至被包庇和称赞。可见国内司法环境的败坏、国人价值观的扭曲。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n你法我笑<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTBhZjFlZmRiYzhiZjE3MTU4MjBjLnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEzMzQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/50af1efdbc8bf1715820c.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/50af1efdbc8bf1715820c.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/50af1efdbc8bf1715820c.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTk0Njk1NGI4MTRkZmQzNWIwNmQ1LnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEzMzQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a946954b814dfd35b06d5.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a946954b814dfd35b06d5.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a946954b814dfd35b06d5.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYzA4NzcyOWM5ODExOGI1M2E2NTJmLnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEzMzQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c087729c98118b53a652f.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c087729c98118b53a652f.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c087729c98118b53a652f.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDFhNDQyNzNkNmJlYTc4MzkwZTQzLnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEzMzQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/01a44273d6bea78390e43.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/01a44273d6bea78390e43.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/01a44273d6bea78390e43.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMjI3MzlhOGM4ZmExNWEzOTJlZTk0LnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEzMzQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/22739a8c8fa15a392ee94.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/22739a8c8fa15a392ee94.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/22739a8c8fa15a392ee94.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNmQ5NDY1ZTdhYzE2NjUxYWUwNTlmLmpwZz93aWR0aD0zODAmaGVpZ2h0PTI0Nw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6d9465e7ac16651ae059f.jpg?width=380&amp;height=247\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6d9465e7ac16651ae059f.jpg?width=380&amp;height=247\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6d9465e7ac16651ae059f.jpg?width=380&amp;height=247\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
